 certification examination"]},{slug:"intensive",level:"Live",title:"The Intensive",track:"Instructor-Led \xB7 2 weeks",status:"forge",blurb:"A live, instructor-led program for traders who want the method taught directly. Six cohorts a year, capped for attention.",outcomes:["Learn the method live from a certified instructor","Work real setups in cohort","Leave evaluation-ready"]},{slug:"confluence",level:"Tool",title:"TDC Confluence Indicator",track:"TradingView \xB7 $29/mo \xB7 $249/yr \xB7 $399 lifetime",status:"forge",blurb:"The method on your chart. Four timeframes you choose, each reading the validated TDC signals, rolled into one weighted verdict by higher-timeframe dominance \u2014 and an honest NO TRADE when the top timeframes disagree. Paid, source-protected.",outcomes:["See timeframe agreement at a glance","Trade only when the doctrine confirms","Get a glanceable read of the method you're learning"]}];function S({go:t}){return React.createElement(React.Fragment,null,React.createElement("section",{style:{maxWidth:1080,margin:"0 auto",padding:"84px 28px 56px",display:"grid",gridTemplateColumns:"1.4fr 1fr",gap:48,alignItems:"center"}},React.createElement("div",null,React.createElement("p",{className:"h-sans",style:{letterSpacing:".18em",textTransform:"uppercase",fontSize:12,color:e.oxblood,margin:"0 0 22px"}},"TDC Academy \xB7 A Trading Doctrine"),React.createElement("h1",{style:{fontWeight:700,fontSize:50,lineHeight:1.08,margin:"0 0 22px"}},"A method built to be proven, taught, and held to standard."),React.createElement("p",{style:{fontSize:18,lineHeight:1.6,maxWidth:"62ch",margin:"0 0 18px"}},"The Demetri Code is not another set of indicators. It is an operating doctrine for the market \u2014 wave structure, Fibonacci, and price behavior organized into procedures a disciplined trader can repeat. Every rule earns its place by surviving a test against real market data. What cannot be measured does not become doctrine."),React.createElement("p",{style:{fontSize:18,lineHeight:1.6,maxWidth:"62ch",margin:"0 0 30px"}},"The Academy teaches that doctrine the way a profession is taught: with a textbook, qualification standards, examinations, and a credential that means something."),React.createElement("div",{style:{display:"flex",gap:14,flexWrap:"wrap"}},React.createElement(Btn,{primary:!0,onClick:()=>t("waitlist")},"Join the Roll"),React.createElement(Btn,{onClick:()=>t("philosophy")},"Read the Doctrine"))),React.createElement("div",{style:{display:"flex",justifyContent:"center"}},React.createElement(h,{size:230}))),React.createElement("section",{style:{background:e.parchmentDeep,borderTop:`1px solid ${e.line}`,borderBottom:`1px solid ${e.line}`}},React.createElement("div",{style:{maxWidth:1080,margin:"0 auto",padding:"56px 28px",display:"grid",gridTemplateColumns:"repeat(3, 1fr)",gap:40}},React.createElement(m,{n:"I",title:"A doctrine, not a tip sheet"},"The method is written down, version-controlled, and defended. Each procedure traces to a tested observation, not to a personality or a hunch."),React.createElement(m,{n:"II",title:"Taught like a profession"},"Textbook, study guides, qualification standards, and examinations. You progress through measured competencies, not a playlist of videos."),React.createElement(m,{n:"III",title:"A credential with weight"},"Certification is earned and held to standard. It is meant to signal real, demonstrated capability \u2014 a credential you carry, not a badge to decorate a screenshot."))),React.createElement("section",{style:{maxWidth:1080,margin:"0 auto",padding:"64px 28px 8px"}},React.createElement("p",{className:"h-sans",style:{letterSpacing:".18em",textTransform:"uppercase",fontSize:12,color:e.oxblood,margin:"0 0 6px"}},"The Path"),React.createElement("h2",{style:{fontWeight:700,fontSize:30,margin:"0 0 24px"}},"Three levels, then the credential."),React.createElement("div",{style:{display:"grid",gridTemplateColumns:"repeat(4,1fr)",gap:18}},c.map(i=>React.createElement("button",{key:i.slug,onClick:()=>t("course",i.slug),className:"card",style:{textAlign:"left",cursor:"pointer",padding:"18px",color:e.ink,fontFamily:p}},React.createElement("div",{className:"h-sans",style:{fontSize:11,letterSpacing:".1em",textTransform:"uppercase",color:e.gold,marginBottom:8}},i.level),React.createElement("div",{className:"h-sans",style:{fontWeight:700,fontSize:17,marginBottom:6}},i.title),React.createElement("div",{style:{fontSize:14,lineHeight:1.5,opacity:.85}},i.track))))),React.createElement("section",{style:{maxWidth:820,margin:"0 auto",padding:"56px 28px 72px",textAlign:"center"}},React.createElement("hr",{className:"rule-gold",style:{margin:"0 auto 26px"}}),React.createElement("h2",{style:{fontWeight:700,fontSize:26,margin:"0 0 16px"}},"The materials are still in the forge."),React.createElement("p",{style:{fontSize:18,lineHeight:1.6}},"We are finishing the work that earns the name \u2014 putting every rule through validation before it is taught. The textbook, guides, and courses open when that work is done, not before. Join the roll and you will be first to know, and first in line."),React.createElement("div",{style:{marginTop:28}},React.createElement(Btn,{primary:!0,onClick:()=>t("waitlist")},"Join the Roll"))))}function m({n:t,title:i,children:a}){return React.createElement("div",null,React.createElement("div",{style:{fontSize:42,color:e.gold,lineHeight:1,marginBottom:10}},t),React.createElement("h3",{className:"h-sans",style:{fontSize:18,fontWeight:700,margin:"0 0 10px"}},i),React.createElement("p",{style:{fontSize:16,lineHeight:1.55,margin:0}},a))}function k(){return React.createElement(Article,{label:"The Doctrine",title:"What The Demetri Code is, and how it is built"},React.createElement("p",null,"Most trading education sells confidence. It hands you a pattern, asserts that it works, and moves on. The Demetri Code is built on the opposite premise: a claim is worth nothing until it has been tested, and a rule that cannot be measured has no business being taught."),React.createElement("p",null,"The method is an integrated reading of the market. Wave structure tells you where you are. Fibonacci tells you where price is likely to act. Market structure \u2014 the breaks and the changes of character \u2014 tells you when the read has confirmed or failed. These are not five systems bolted together; they are one way of seeing, organized into procedures for the two states a market is ever in: trending, and correcting."),React.createElement(H2,null,"Operating and Casualty Procedures"),React.createElement("p",null,"When the market trends, it rewards a different posture than when it corrects. The doctrine names these plainly. Operating Procedures govern the trending market, where the method is at its most reliable and a trader presses a validated edge. Casualty Procedures govern the corrective market, where the discipline is preservation \u2014 reduce, survive, and re-enter with force only when the trend genuinely resumes. Knowing which state you are in is the first decision of every session, and the most consequential."),React.createElement(H2,null,"How a rule earns its place"),React.createElement("p",null,"Behind every rule a student is taught sits a chain the student never has to see. An observation begins as a hypothesis. It is put through a falsification test against years of real price data, where it is confirmed, refined, or thrown out. What survives becomes a theory \u2014 an explanation of why the market behaves this way \u2014 and only then is it written as a rule a trader can act on. The grade rides with the rule for its whole life, so the institution always knows how much weight a given instruction can bear."),React.createElement("p",null,"This is slower than asserting a method and selling it. It is also the only way to build something that survives its founder. The materials open when this work is finished, because teaching an unproven rule would betray the whole point."))}function T({go:t}){return React.createElement(Article,{label:"Curriculum",title:"A progression, not a playlist"},React.createElement("p",null,"The Academy is organized the way a serious profession trains its people: in levels, each with defined competencies you must demonstrate before you advance. Every lesson maps to a specific piece of execution logic. Nothing is taught for completeness; everything is taught because it changes how you act at the hard right edge of the chart."),c.filter(i=>i.slug!=="intensive").map(i=>React.createElement("div",{key:i.slug,style:{borderLeft:`3px solid ${e.gold}`,padding:"4px 0 4px 20px",margin:"26px 0"}},React.createElement("h3",{className:"h-sans",style:{fontSize:19,fontWeight:700,margin:"0 0 8px"}},i.level," \u2014 ",i.title),React.createElement("p",{style:{margin:0,lineHeight:1.6}},i.blurb))),React.createElement("p",{style:{marginTop:28}},React.createElement(Btn,{onClick:()=>t("catalog")},"See the full catalog")))}function C({go:t}){const[i,a]=d("All"),o=["All","Self-Study","Self-Guided","Instructor-Led"],r=c.filter(n=>i==="All"||n.track.includes(i));return React.createElement("section",{style:{maxWidth:1080,margin:"0 auto",padding:"72px 28px"}},React.createElement("p",{className:"h-sans",style:{letterSpacing:".18em",textTransform:"uppercase",fontSize:12,color:e.oxblood,margin:"0 0 12px"}},"Courses"),React.createElement("h1",{style:{fontWeight:700,fontSize:40,margin:"0 0 14px"}},"The catalog"),React.createElement("p",{style:{fontSize:18,lineHeight:1.6,maxWidth:"64ch",marginBottom:28}},"Each program is in production now. None will be sold until the method behind it has cleared validation. Join the roll to be told the moment each one opens."),React.createElement("div",{style:{display:"flex",gap:10,marginBottom:28,flexWrap:"wrap"}},o.map(n=>React.createElement("button",{key:n,onClick:()=>a(n),className:"h-sans",style:{cursor:"pointer",fontSize:12,letterSpacing:".06em",textTransform:"uppercase",padding:"8px 14px",border:`1px solid ${i===n?e.oxblood:e.ink+"40"}`,backgrou